description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Gatinho purrs with a rating of 82, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 164, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, 8 for East, 3 for South, and Leverage for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50822-38362-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [164 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
